00:41:42.470 --> 00:41:46.079
I would think of all the people I've ever
worked with that I loved working with

00:41:46.079 --> 00:41:49.569
and they'd all be on the job.

00:41:49.569 --> 00:41:54.349
And then I would make a list of people
