You've got Meryl Streep and Joel Edgerton,
C.J. and

00:43:43.059 --> 00:43:46.430
John Tolz as your DP, and you can shoot it
in your hometown."

00:43:46.430 --> 00:43:47.430
BOOM!

00:43:47.430 --> 00:43:49.859
I'm --I'm--I'm going [makes rocket and explosion
noises]--I got ideas.

00:43:49.859 --> 00:43:50.859
&gt;&gt;Joel: I'm already in Iowa.

00:43:50.859 --> 00:43:51.859
&gt;&gt;Peter: You're already there.

00:43:51.859 --> 00:43:52.859
&gt;&gt;Joel: I'm already there.

00:43:52.859 --> 00:43:53.859
[laughter]

00:43:53.859 --> 00:43:56.009
&gt;&gt;Peter: And Meryl's very happy to be working
