00:45:34.019 --> 00:45:35.019
But if I have one, thank you.

00:45:35.019 --> 00:45:37.780
I love working there.

00:45:37.780 --> 00:45:41.950
It's a great
place to work, but I just don't have a story."

00:45:41.950 --> 00:45:42.950
That was fine.

00:45:42.950 --> 00:45:47.859
A couple days later I had a lunch, or not
