00:45:47.859 --> 00:45:51.440
Scott Sanders who brought
along another producer Ahmet Zappa.

00:45:51.440 --> 00:45:54.089
And Ahmet Zappa said, "Can I tell you a story?"

00:45:54.089 --> 00:45:59.099
He said, "I was in the shower, and this idea
came to me, and I want to tell it to you."

00:45:59.099 --> 00:46:02.700
And he told it to me, started about the couple
who can't have a kid and they plant the ideas

00:46:02.700 --> 00:46:06.619
about the kid in the
ground and I went, "Stop.

00:46:06.619 --> 00:46:07.619
I don't want to hear anymore.

00:46:07.619 --> 00:46:08.619
I'm in.

00:46:08.619 --> 00:46:09.769
I got it."

00:46:09.769 --> 00:46:14.450
And I basically adopted that idea and ran
